      "content": "For a universally accepted baseline, consider the following core rules for dressing and grooming:\n\n* For men:\n\t+ A well-fitted, simple suit in neutral colors (black, navy, gray) with a crisp white shirt and a slim tie\n\t+ Polished dress shoes, black or brown\n\t+ Simple, classic watch and a simple leather belt\n\t+ Groomed hair and a clean shave (if applicable)\n* For women:\n\t+ A classic, tailored pantsuit or a skirt suit in neutral colors (black, navy, gray) with a crisp white blouse\n\t+ Closed-toe, low-to-moderate heels and polished shoes\n\t+ Simple jewelry (classical watch, simple necklace, stud earrings)\n\t+ Polished nails and a neat hairstyle\n\nThese basic standards convey professionalism and sophistication, and can be adapted to different cultural and regional settings while still being universally recognizable as \"high-end.\"",
