      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's interesting how those rules are so specific. i noticed they're mostly focused on Western styles like suits and blazers. if someone is at a high-end event in say, india or japan, or even parts of africa, would they need to adjust these \"standard\" rules to stay sophisticated, or is the suit-and-tie look still the primary way to be seen as professional there?",
